How to work on Chat Bot

Heinlein bot, inject Robert Heinlein's political opinions
into the bot.


The sun also rises chatbot?
There is a lot of dialogue, in theory I could try to break it down and assign dialogue lines to characters

The issue is the copyright. I really, really do not want to infringe on anyone's copyright. Working on contemporary
or recently generated data runs into so many potential not just legal, but ethical issues. I feel far more comfortable
working on something that's basically 100 years old or more, even though it's harder to make sense of, given the time gap
and all the cultural changes since then.

Characters:

-Narrator, aka Jake
-Robert Cohn
-Lady Ashley, first name Brett
- Frances




